OL,4,Closses in the farming sector in Wales
OL,6,FA Welsh government commissioned report
OL,7,Fon a consultation of its own future
OL,8,Fflagship Sustainable Farming Scheme
OL,9,Fsays nearly #200 million could be lost
OL,10,Ffrom Welsh farm business income.
OL,12,FThe report titled 'Potential economic
OL,13,Feffects of the Sustainable Farming
OL,14,FScheme Phase 4JUniversal Actions
OL,15,FModelling Results' was carried out by
OL,16,FADAS, Pareto Consulting SRUCJand
OL,17,FUniversity College Dublin.
